OL,3,CSextortion victim shares story of
OL,4,Cthreats to share intimate images
OL,6,FA man who fell victim as a teenager to
OL,7,Fcriminals demanding money from him and
OL,8,Fthreatening to share his intimate
OL,9,Fimages has opened up about his ordeal.
OL,11,FThe man, who ITV News are calling
OL,12,FPeter, was 13 when he became a victim
OL,13,Fof sextortion after believing he was
OL,14,Ftalking to a girl online.
OL,16,FHe was manipulated into exposing
OL,17,Fhimself and was told that his intimate
OL,18,Fpictures would be shared with his
OL,19,Ffamily, unless Peter sent them more
OL,20,Fexplicit pictures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
