PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777539988
OL,3,CSextortion victim shares story of
OL,4,Cthreats to share intimate images
OL,6,FThe abuse only stopped when he told
OL,7,Fhis mother.
OL,9,FPeter was spending time on Skype
OL,10,Fwithin a gaming community and
OL,11,Fregularly speaking to people he did
OL,12,Fnot know. He was contacted online and
OL,13,Fwas led to believe someone was
OL,14,Finterested in him.
OL,16,FPeter said: "I remember someone saying
OL,17,Fthis girl was keen, and I added her on
OL,18,FSkype. I thought I was talking to
OL,19,Fsomeone my age ` I had no idea it was
OL,20,Fgoing to turn into blackmail."
OL,26,@xD@MOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
