FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777539988
OL,3,CSextortion victim shares story of
OL,4,Cthreats to share intimate images
OL,6,FPeter explained that the situation
OL,7,Fescalated quickly. His Skype account
OL,8,Fwas linked to Facebook and his friends
OL,9,Flist was public, with comments and
OL,10,Flikes on photos revealing family
OL,11,Fmembers ` which the offender then used
OL,12,Fto threaten him.
OL,14,FHe said: "It felt like the whole thing
OL,15,Fturned on its head. I was shocked, and
OL,16,Fat 13 it was hard to process. The
OL,17,Fthreat of them sending it to my family
OL,18,Fwas terrifying."
OL,26,@vD@JOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
