CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777539988
OL,3,CSextortion victim shares story of
OL,4,Cthreats to share intimate images
OL,6,FAfter a brief period, Peter told his
OL,7,Fmum, who supported him and challenged
OL,8,Fthe offender over Skype. The contact
OL,9,Fthen stopped.
OL,11,FPeter says it has only become easier
OL,12,Fto speak about his experience in
OL,13,Frecent years and he now realises how
OL,14,Fmuch it affected him, including
OL,15,Fshaping his interest in privacy and
OL,16,Fcyber security.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
