PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777539988
OL,3,CSextortion victim shares story of
OL,4,Cthreats to share intimate images
OL,6,FHe added: "At the time I didn't report
OL,7,Fit, but I wish I had. Reporting gives
OL,8,Fthe police a chance to identify
OL,9,Foffenders and stop them harming other
OL,10,Fpeople."
OL,12,FMerseyside Police dealt with 575 cases
OL,13,Fin the 11 months up to September 2025,
OL,14,Fwith more male teenagers being
OL,15,Ftargeted.
OL,17,FDetective Sergeant Danny Gavin said
OL,18,Fthe force is stepping up enforcement
OL,19,Fand prevention activity to tackle
OL,20,Fsextortion and encouraging people to
OL,21,Fcome forward.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@HO]
