OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1777539988
OL,3,CSextortion victim shares story of
OL,4,Cthreats to share intimate images
OL,6,FDS Gavin said: "Sextortion is
OL,7,Fblackmail. Offenders use threats and
OL,8,Fcoercion to try to control victims,
OL,9,Fand we want people to know they will
OL,10,Fbe taken seriously and supported if
OL,11,Fthey report.
OL,13,F"Our specialist investigators are
OL,14,Frelentless in their pursuit of
OL,15,Foffenders. We'll follow the evidence
OL,16,Fwherever it leads, and work across
OL,17,Fborders when we need to, to identify
OL,18,Foffenders and put them before the
OL,19,Fcourts."
OL,26,@nD@POUuD@AOU{D@HO]
